{"tid":2322694,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如何對抗香港廢老、「長輩」持老賣老既社會問題","createTime":"2020-12-12T13:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T16:06:24.000Z","uid":299938,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb75cec4de0ff1f03516d619c99c6ec64ea3c8b","tid":2322694,"uid":299938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得亞洲有個好大既社會問題就係我標題所講既個個，好多人係網上鬧，但現實生活都係唔敢講。由「關愛座」變廢老座，公司老屎忽，由婆家外母家問題（我的極品四大長老），去到窮廢老生仔（生你），再蝦蝦霸霸既問題，全部都緊貼我地生活。到底要點先可以引起廢老既注意，同佢地講「你地食得鹽多唔撚係大哂」，改變佢地既垃圾觀念？歡迎各位受害者黎分享一下。"},{"pid":"a0e3f1ef9ebdc8084881a2b2d9facc04952d55ad","tid":2322694,"uid":299938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5bc198806fe2e06004b97f7a53f6b830c070660","tid":2322694,"uid":299938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97f56884bf084c53b9f9c1c1adb733098b2eea1","tid":2322694,"uid":299938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a447e21d55f63f1975d3899efb3f24e17e9fb88","tid":2322694,"uid":299938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5f204c68479a7fc7284edbfa408d579e4686fc","tid":2322694,"uid":299938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1af5d5d9247db1a837d19294c03af4eb6b8976","tid":2322694,"uid":299938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad78b15a13233b7c1420389f99390890e25ddf8","tid":2322694,"ui